<div id="topofpage" style="visibility:hidden"></div>



<p><em>This hearty Chinese-inspired Instant Pot Lo Mein noodles recipe features an umami-rich blend of oyster sauce, soy sauce, sesame oil, and red chili flakes.  The tender beef is tossed together with noodles and broccoli to make a healthy one-pot meal that&rsquo;s quick and requires minimal cleanup!</em></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image"><img decoding="async" width="683" height="1024" fetchpriority="high" src="https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-683x1024.jpg" alt="Instant Pot Lo Mein with Beef and Broccoli in black bowl on straw mat with chopsticks laid across bowl - Paint the Kitchen Red" data-skip-lazy class="wp-image-9854" srcset="https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-200x300.jpg 200w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-720x1080.jpg 720w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-360x540.jpg 360w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-180x270.jpg 180w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-150x225.jpg 150w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red.jpg 1697w" sizes="(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px" data-pin-media="https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/