-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail" alt="Instant Pot Lo Mein with Beef and Broccoli in black bowl on straw mat with chopsticks laid across bowl - Paint the Kitchen Red" srcset="https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-720x720.jpg 720w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-360x360.jpg 360w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-180x180.jpg 180w, https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red-96x96.jpg 96w" sizes="(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px" data-pin-media="https://www.paintthekitchenred.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Instant-Pot-Lo-Mein-with-Beef-and-Broccoli-P1-Paint-the-Kitchen-Red.jpg"></noscript></div>
