<h2 class="wprm-recipe-name wprm-block-text-bold">Instant Pot Lo Mein Noodles with Beef and Broccoli</h2>


<div class="wprm-spacer"></div>
<div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">This hearty Chinese-inspired Instant Pot Lo Mein noodles recipe features an umami-rich blend of oyster sauce, soy sauce, sesame oil, and red chili flakes. The tender beef is tossed together with noodles and broccoli to make a healthy one-pot meal that&rsquo;s quick and requires minimal cleanup!</span></div>

