    <div class="wprm-recipe-summary wprm-block-text-normal"><span style="display: block;">If you're looking for that last-minute accompaniment to complete your dinner menu and you don't have a lot of time, this Instant Pot Fried Rice is perfect for you.&nbsp; Quick and easy, the recipe calls for frozen vegetables, Jasmine rice, and ingredients you probably have on hand and it requires minimal prep work.</span></div>
